                <p class="text-muted">To be your go-to online store, offering everything you need in one place.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="p-4 border rounded-3 shadow-sm h-100">
                <h5>Our Mission</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Delivering quality, affordability, and convenience with every order.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="p-4 border rounded-3 shadow-sm h-100">
                <h5>Our Promise</h5>
                <p class="text-muted">Customer satisfaction is at the heart of everything we do.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
